{"type": "article", "id": 20139, "title": "想想过去一年，我又学会这 17 种无用的技能", "description": "谢谢一同学习的好奇心读者们。", "date": "2016-01-03T08:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 3, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 161, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702101244N0E3Z2MzHXYUbiV5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1. 元旦，挑 9 张照片发朋友圈，说这是我的 2015，然后煽情地许来年愿望。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101228gmhPb7SGHwOUrWzV.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"267\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.55625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"><strong>2. 快速找到一部想看的剧/电影。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101230gJ1pMld79ebZUXWB.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"675\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>3. 练就一身高超的挤地铁本领  @ Dr_Foxx</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101231kTiv45V2qxRoSgMJ.gif\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56181818\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>4. 下班了，喝水都高兴。 @ 阳光-Mermaid</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101235u8kM42o0AOPpilz1.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"240\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.48\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>5. 单身汪生存技能。@ 董小姐</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101235JwDsuQlgfCk573Zm.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"584\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.54074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>6. 有人惹毛了我，我能在他们走开 10 分钟后想出一个绝妙的还击。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101236p2U3vGL4iPVbcDr6.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"216\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.432\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>7. 静静地看别人装 X。 @ Miffy</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101237Vrq0HYZlQCFufJsI.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>8. 我能辨认出哪个下载按钮是真正的下载按钮了。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150354TWHavFjuGxkRlJVh.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>9. 在网上找到各种奇怪的网站以及视频资源。 @时间~逆</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021012371wcTGgydkX8AQUFJ.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.564\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>10. 不愿做的事情 10 秒钟就能找到合适借口不去做。 @朱向华</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101237wgR5DI9nOXClWcbk.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" title=\"@\" alt=\"@\" data-ratio=\"0.585\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>11. 在三次以内正确输入 12306 的验证码…… @石雨峰</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101238E3buwpLXHIYvUTBZ.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.42083333\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>12. 终于理解了钱的重要性。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101239XIUP9vdEl8wgGbmf.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"369\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.738\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>13. 知道了可以保存二维码再识别。@[ F D͛ L ]</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101240qt0TPhMFKNiomvsQ.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75117371\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>14. </strong><strong>提取公积金 @</strong><strong>Aurora赵</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101242d2oYMbEjFVIQNkK1.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>15. </strong><strong>无聊的时候就下载各种 app，后来再也没用。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021012437nArJ8YhGqdM6CVB.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>16. 同时看 3 个台的跨年晚会。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150356L2rhQxbdqilGzaE9.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"503\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.62875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>17. 有谁不服，颐和园后面有一野湖。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021012447mTbxk2UOJa6NpCW.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"758\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.70185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}